bottomAxis.description: Indicate which axis to display the bottom of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object ChartsXAxisProps.

colors.description: Color palette used to colorize multiple series.

leftAxis.description: Indicate which axis to display the left of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object ChartsYAxisProps.

rightAxis.description: Indicate which axis to display the right of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object ChartsYAxisProps.

slotProps.description: The props used for each component slot.

topAxis.description: Indicate which axis to display the top of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object ChartsXAxisProps.
